title: G1 Any Role LF Team

embed.description: Create & discover new Champion builds/strategies, check your Summoner statistics and try our powerful LoL charts.

body:
Hi, name's Milo. I'm 19.

I'm Gold 1 and have been climbing the soloQ ladder, hopefully I'll be Plat soon.

I can play any role, but if I had to pick one I would be support.

I'm friendly and will probably be on alot during the holidays, wouldn't mind finding a team for the open tournament.
